ACT 1
=====

Scene 1
=======
[Enter Leonato, Governor of Messina, Hero his daughter,
and Beatrice his niece, with a Messenger.]


LEONATO, [with a letter]  I learn in this letter that Don
Pedro of Aragon comes this night to Messina.

